<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>On Sunday she stepped out for the photocall of the Miu Miu Women's Tales short film series.</p>

<p>And Nathalie Emmanuel was keen to continue her promotional tour for the release as she stepped out in a shirt from the brand when she arrived in style at the Revenge Room premiere on Monday.</p>

<p>The Game of Thrones star, 31, put on a stylish display in the white logo t-shirt which she paired with a sleek blue skirt for a casually chic look.</p>

<p>Stylish: Nathalie Emmanuel looked casually chic in a Miu Miu t-shirt and a sleek blue skirt as she arrived in style at the 77th Venice Film Festival on Monday</p>

<p>Nathalie boosted her height in a pair of sparkling silver heels, and complemented her look by accessorising with a silver cross-body bag.</p>

<p>Her brunette locks were styled in natural curls that framed her face well, and she added a glittering touch to the look by wearing a pair of pearl earrings. </p>

<p>Nathalie went solo for the event, after previously being seen in Venice with her actor beau, Alex Lanipekun. </p>

<p>Fashionista: Nathalie boosted her height in a pair of sparkling silver heels, and complemented her look by accessorising with a silver cross-body bag</p>

<p>Stunning: Nathalie's brunette locks were styled in natural curls that framed her face well, and she added a glittering touch to the look by wearing a pair of pearl earrings</p>

<p>The thespian couple were rumoured to be dating in 2018, and news of their relationship became official when they were seen putting on a loved up display at the Ischia Film Festival in Italy that same year. </p>

<p>They have been spotted at multiple events since, but they prefer to keep their relationship private and out of the limelight.</p>

<p>Prior to her relationship with Alex, Nathalie was linked to Devon Anderson who is known for playing Billie Jackson in EastEnders.</p>

<p>Couple goals: Nathalie went solo for the event, after previously being seen in Venice with her actor beau, Alex Lanipekun on Sunday (pictured)</p>

<p>They met on set of the soap drama, Hollyoaks, where Nathalie joined the cast in 2006 to play Sasha Valentine and she quickly rose to fame. </p>

<p>She was kept busy with her first major role as her character battled heroin addiction and turned to prostitution. </p>

<p>Nathalie appeared on the soap until 2010 and went onto land roles in blockbuster films such as Maze Runner, Furious 7 from the Fast &amp; Furious franchise. </p>

<p>Iconic: The Venice Film Festival is one of the world's oldest award ceremonies and is listed as one of the 'Big Five' events </p>

<p>Quiet: Though the event is still taking place, it is a markedly toned down affair to previous years amid the coronavirus crisis</p>

<p>Eerie: The festival hall looked quiet in the evening</p>
